    "description": "《忘却前夜》是一款克苏鲁题材改编的Roguelite卡牌构筑游戏。你将在游戏中链接性格迥异的唤醒体，构筑专属于你的策略牌组，探索迷雾地图、遭遇随机事件、享受卡牌战斗的策略刺激，并一步步调查诡异而疯狂的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/12f558883075b344773d64977df1c9be.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=274 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【世界观】</h2>这个世界正在死去，而人们对此一无所知。<br>面对这隐秘而不可名状的灾厄，你将作为守密人，唤醒与与灾厄同源的力量，链接游走在疯狂边缘的人形武器，来抵抗这一场浩大的危机。<br>如果一切终将被遗忘，你是否愿意作为世界存在过的证明，背负秘密，一路前行？<br>墓碑为证，愿银钥指引前路。<br>欢迎入学，守密人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/36fdb98da2dc10bb8b1366fc86d12a8c.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=276 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2>● 独特二次元画风，丰富各异的群像角色，自克苏鲁文化衍生的海量设计，满足你丰富喜好！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/8cebd6d0505adf61555bcc57a077a855.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/8cebd6d0505adf61555bcc57a077a855.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/8cebd6d0505adf61555bcc57a077a855.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/96ebd8335b16b2a3fbc7745963501e52.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/96ebd8335b16b2a3fbc7745963501e52.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/96ebd8335b16b2a3fbc7745963501e52.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 四大基础界域，185+且仍在持续扩展的牌库阵容，丰富的流派体验，打造策略的广度和深度，让你自由构筑专属牌组，体验以小博大的策略乐趣！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/ca00f9f8d3018dec42daa760a7e64240.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/ca00f9f8d3018dec42daa760a7e64240.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/ca00f9f8d3018dec42daa760a7e64240.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/3cac670978e95a4847650b1b52ef7fa9.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/3cac670978e95a4847650b1b52ef7fa9.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/3cac670978e95a4847650b1b52ef7fa9.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 轻肉鸽、低门槛、高耐玩！让你轻松上手，重复可玩！<br>地图事件、掉落物品、卡牌buff、商店刷新……随机出百变战局，每一关都有新惊喜与新挑战！<br>局外角色养成、构筑阵容，局内死亡抵抗、应急灵知，让新手体验更可控、更轻松、更友好！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/f9aa2ebe6bc86a75e1badac386600b7c.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/f9aa2ebe6bc86a75e1badac386600b7c.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/f9aa2ebe6bc86a75e1badac386600b7c.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/94c00e73e21e97ee605fd2f267353039.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/94c00e73e21e97ee605fd2f267353039.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/94c00e73e21e97ee605fd2f267353039.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 触动人心的剧情与配乐，单元剧情一步步走向疯狂的真相与深渊，展现黑暗绝境中的人性群像与不屈微光。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/fae3dcee7af91fab7a201384b20299a3.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/fae3dcee7af91fab7a201384b20299a3.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/fae3dcee7af91fab7a201384b20299a3.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 单机爬塔挑战烧脑极限；而PVP玩法颠覆体验，全新的卡牌效果与机制，无需养成，上手即玩，享受公正的对战乐趣！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/711c6cfb985992f4d1ef186436e9fcba.poster.avif?t=1739300850\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/711c6cfb985992f4d1ef186436e9fcba.webm?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/711c6cfb985992f4d1ef186436e9fcba.mp4?t=1739300850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【这里是来自制作组的留言】</h2>感谢各位来玩《忘却前夜》！没有什么比你愿意尝试我们的游戏更令人高兴了。如果你喜欢《忘却前夜》，或者有任何体验反馈，都欢迎告诉我们！<br>虽然这个世界充满危机，但很高兴我们能相遇。<br>愿银钥指引前路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052450/extras/3b4065e3f2929c4c9ac45cf6fde5b3e8.avif?t=1739300850\" width=586 height=368 /></span>",
